{"tid":1679042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家馬路冇晒D欄河真係好危險","createTime":"2019-10-28T03:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T04:15:27.000Z","uid":10901,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"037669edf725b395db9c1c3efdfdb563094cc689","tid":1679042,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"大家應該瘋狂1823叫政府整返!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e84dcc6c90ffa0150090018fa33273cbbb12af1","tid":1679042,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f59ff17578f5606783ac929a2cef40b250475b43","tid":1679042,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6ce9c2730771796e5fb3b396978d2b8296a7ba","tid":1679042,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"真係好危險囉<br />\n<br />\n要打1823搞搞佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2d78d28dbb56fd696d27619922e2f442b41f6c","tid":1679042,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽 5毛大軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD58eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=bc1fc0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"e423b765f46e70b9d8d3e262aba5a791643bb681","tid":1679042,"uid":69419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"首先假設可以召喚二百萬人，當每一百個人就有一個勇武<br />\n198萬人去港島遊，大型遊行係畫面撚一路想要既野，亦可以做distraction<br />\n<br />\n當日港島（連登吹雞）以零gear/少量gear 和理大遊行拉仇恨值,行傳統路線，定終點為政總，一定要佔路同唱歌，同時引晒防暴速龍戒備。唔係放棄港島，係用港島牽制，和理非用和平集會就幫到手唔會托手踭，最多呼籲長期抗爭，確保物資充裕。班黑警一定好想離開港島，所以要一步一步向西環推進，佢地又要保春袋留低。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">和理目標：港島創造200萬人遊行畫面，牽制恐怖分子主力，協助癱瘓三隧（bonus: 西環搾春袋）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n見到港島出防暴速龍出晒，呢一刻各區勇武出擊，先以一百人為一隊聚集（tg協調），達成以下三個目標，<br />\n1.爆晒全部黨鐵站（甚至狗屋），以列車為目標，<br />\n2. 正式封三隧，手段可以係塞車、燒政府車，偷政府車撞牆等，之後要向大老山隧道，獅子山隧道，城門隧道同屯門公路出手，吐露港公路，大埔道<br />\n3.狂爆狗屋，火魔術師主攻同結界師牽制，控場用工兵隊set RB。（對人用水魔效果更佳）<br />\n優先次序：<br />\nI. 觀塘、紅磡、尖沙咀<br />\nII. 將軍澳、黃大仙、旺角、深水埗、沙田<br />\n放棄新界係因為我地打唔到，太遠太大唔着數。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武目標：確實地癱瘓交通（先封入港島既路、再封新界入九龍既路），解除每區恐怖分子武裝力量，得到武裝力量，積極籌備支援港島</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻政府一定話暴動乜柒乜柒，懇請現屆議員、民眾議會同民間記者會合作，政府話幾時搞記招，你就宣布幾時搞。民議會宣布正式取代現時管治班子，希望用制度內既手段解決問題。你話我on9都好，要有條件承認鬼國主權。但要滿足以下先決條件。<br />\n1）舉行真&bull;雙普選，落實高度自治<br />\n2）解散現行政府，以一人一票方式重新籌劃<br />\n3）解散警隊，追究一切警暴責任<br />\n4）釋放所有政治監禁者, 徹銷政治檢控<br />\n5）確立中國主權及香港自治地位，永久不變，承接外交及國防責任。<br />\n（澳洲/加拿大模式）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">議員民記民議目標：確立所有訴求，架空現有政府，確立自治地位，成立屬於香港人既政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後一步，以安全為先，勇武重開西隧去港島合流，向金鐘推進，以武力制服所有黑警。和理要向西環繼續推進協助勇武手足，擊潰殘餘黑警勢力。<br />\n<br />\n還望那天共聚煲底，<br />\n和勇手足除罩相見。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b74d8bb77afed14bc27ae886544bbefe9a24770f","tid":1679042,"uid":35365,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"有d地方過馬路方便咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614354982ed7918d913544a4b0640e57b8c0e3f1","tid":1679042,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74d8bb77afed14bc27ae886544bbefe9a24770f","tid":1679042,"uid":35365,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"有d地方過馬路方便咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211228944130ee6da570b21cbf8e90a844495e38","tid":1679042,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74d8bb77afed14bc27ae886544bbefe9a24770f","tid":1679042,"uid":35365,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"有d地方過馬路方便咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"有人講過某d安全島係細到唔合理，冇左欄先正路"},{"pid":"f5447f64a795b0e0cebb58d60c6b4a038a48663f","tid":1679042,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037669edf725b395db9c1c3efdfdb563094cc689","tid":1679042,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"大家應該瘋狂1823叫政府整返!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"